The magic is that the company acts as a classic corporate customer to the carrier who orders large quantities of SIM cards.
As a significant customer, he will then receive special price (and other) offers.
The problem is that the terms and conditions of all Czech mobile operators prohibit similar resale.
'If the cases you mention were to occur, it could be a breach of the terms of the contract we were dealing with and could result in the termination of the cooperation with the company in question,' Martina Kemr answered our question on this issue.
However, it is unlikely that such action would not reach the responsible people of mobile operators.
In particular, the three companies mentioned above may have thousands of customers.
